com.camerontec.catalys.server.management.mxbean

Interface ManagedSession

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SessionStateSnapshot
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SessionMXBeanImpl

    @MXBean
public interface ManagedSession
extends SessionStateSnapshot
    Represents an instance of a Catalys Session that has been exposed via JMX. This has not been named Session to avoid confusion.
